{"type":"step-attempt","step":"spec-review","sessionId":"8438592d-35fd-487b-abb9-a7fd429ba788","outcome":{"verdict":"approved","findingsPath":"specrunner/changes/codex-adapter-parity/spec-review-result-001.md","error":null,"toolResult":{"ok":true,"approved":true,"findings":[{"severity":"medium","resolution":"fixable","file":"specrunner/changes/codex-adapter-parity/tasks.md","title":"executeTurn scope ambiguity: described as private class method but needs run() closure","rationale":"T-03 describes executeTurn as a 'private async helper' with 4 parameters, yet it also needs ctx and step which are run() parameters, not class fields. A class-level private method cannot close over them. The implementer must define it as a local arrow function inside run(). The current wording may cause confusion."},{"severity":"low","resolution":"fixable","file":"specrunner/changes/codex-adapter-parity/tasks.md","title":"step:progress test coverage limited to command_execution only","rationale":"T-09 only requires a test case for command_execution. D4 maps four item types (command_execution, file_change, mcp_tool_call, web_search) to progress payloads. The other three have no scenario coverage, leaving D4 partially unverified by tests."},{"severity":"low","resolution":"fixable","file":"specrunner/changes/codex-adapter-parity/spec.md","title":"outputVerification scenario does not assert followUpAttempts accumulation","rationale":"The follow-up violation scenario asserts completionReason and repair turn count but omits followUpAttempts ≥ 1. If this metric is consumed downstream it would be unverified."},{"severity":"low","resolution":"fixable","file":"specrunner/changes/codex-adapter-parity/design.md","title":"extractCodexProgress: command_execution SDK field name not specified","rationale":"D4 says target is the command truncated to ~40 chars but does not name the actual SDK field on the command_execution item. The implementer must verify this against the Codex SDK, risking a silent wrong-field access."}]},"followUpAttempts":1,"transientRetryAttempts":0},"startedAt":"2026-06-12T07:29:44.291Z","endedAt":"2026-06-12T07:32:56.081Z"}
